### Step 7.1: Prepare for GitHub Pages
```bash
# Install Angular CLI for GitHub Pages deployment
ng add angular-cli-ghpages

# Or manually update angular.json
```

**Update `angular.json`:**
```json
{
  "projects": {
    "open-library-app": {
      "architect": {
        "build": {
          "options": {
            "baseHref": "/open-library-app/",
            "outputPath": "dist/open-library-app"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Step 7.2: Build & Deploy
```bash
# Build for production
ng build --configuration production

# Deploy to GitHub Pages
npx angular-cli-ghpages --dir=dist/open-library-app
```

