## COMPLETE QUICK START

```bash
# 1. Create project
ng new open-library-app
cd open-library-app

# 2. Install Tailwind
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p

# 3. Copy all provided code files

# 4. Install dependencies
npm install

# 5. Generate components
ng generate component components/head-bar --skip-tests
ng generate component components/search-bar --skip-tests
ng generate component components/book-list --skip-tests
ng generate component pages/home --skip-tests
ng generate component pages/book-details --skip-tests
ng generate service services/book --skip-tests

# 6. Copy provided TypeScript/HTML/CSS files

# 7. Run dev server
ng serve --open

# 8. Build for production
ng build --configuration production

# 9. Deploy to GitHub Pages
npx angular-cli-ghpages --dir=dist/open-library-app
```

